Dia. 02  If Black Plays
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black plays hane at 1, White can't block directly.
\par White has to pull back and play at 2.
\par The sequence up to 6 is a sente endgame for Black.
\par
\par Whoever plays it is sente, so it is a double sente endgame.
\par
\par
\par }
