\par Same shape is moved to this diagram and the borderlines are made with Xs.
\par It have to be the same borderlines like in \b Dia. 01\b0 .
\par
\par White gets 5 points, Black gets 12 points.
\par
\par After counting
\par (9-5)+(12-10)=6 points.
\par
\par Therefore Black 1 and 3 from the \b main diagram\b0  (or White 1, 3 and 5 from \b Dia. 02\b0 ) is \cf1\b 6 points double sente endgame\cf0\b0 .
